result.formatted_address: 167 Pratas St, Cheung Sha Wan, Hong Kong
result.name: Yuen Long Bistro

reviews.text: They are famous for their thick pork chops. They come with sweet sauce for dipping (sweet soy sauce?) which make them more tasty. Pork chops are juicy and crispy, but a bit oily. For the pork chop with salad/fries set, I didn’t expect it was just one normal size pork chop in a small plate, which wouldn’t make you full for dinner. Do order rice/noodles set if you want a full dinner. Eating here once in awhile would be a good option.
Food still ok, but I the past the pork chop was better.
Decent quality cafe style HK food.

Straight in get one of their pork chop set. The quality of the pork chop is superb given the price. Knife went through like it was a butter.

I had pork chop with spicy minced meat and will go back again.
A good restaurant serving delicious Hong Kong style good. Have lot seats but the good-serving efficiency is poor, really need an improvement.

reviews.text: 大大塊豬扒😋
厚豬扒一流水準😋
招牌菜豬扒飯非常好食, 價錢相宜。
因為關門是零晨3點,我夜收工都有飯食！
早餐叫沙嗲牛肉麵餐,嚟到竟然牛肉係半生熟個湯。碗湯仲要只係暖唔係熱,估計廚房將已解凍牛肉直接放湯出就算。而且再去食其他野質素確比起開張時差咗。唔會再幫襯!

result.formatted_address: 1 Un Chau St, Tong Mi, Hong Kong
result.name: Yuen Long Bistro

reviews.text:
Typical HK cafe fair in a hip setting. Quality of food is average and reasonable portion. About HKD 60 per head for a meal with drinks.

Pork chop is the advertised specialty. It's quite well marinated and is of decent thickness. The baked pork chop rice is OK.

Soup base for the noodle dishes seemed to be powder based though.

Very crowded during lunch time. Service is average at best.

The pork chops they offered here are artificial made, they are not fresh /original real products. The pork chops are their special recommended dish, but they are so oily, really really made people sick.
juicy pock chop
Never coming again. Service was bad, food was horrible.

The most important thing in a HK local cafe is the tea and coffee. Nowadays many of them replace the coffee by using the machine one.  Which makes everything with no style. 
In this experience, at least they offered me to change back to the traditional local coffee. Thanks

result.adr_address: 香港塘尾元州街1號
result.name: 元朗冰室

reviews.text: 三個字快靚正❤️😄
🐷扒最正
服務💪💪

來這裡不吃豬扒包，倒不如不來好了。
豬扒是厚切的，雖然是厚切，可是炸得內部熟透卻不柴，肉汁鮮味四溢，豬肉的香甜夾著包裡特調的配醬，現場上桌馬上吃，真是享受。
厚豬排是兩大件，好好食並配有白飯一碗，一杯飲品，價錢大眾化!
